movie_plot: God Friended Me is an American comedy-drama television series created by Steven Lilien and Bryan Wynbrandt. It stars Brandon Micheal Hall, Violett Beane, Suraj Sharma, Javicia Leslie, Joe Morton and Erica Gimpel.[1] The series was ordered on May 11, 2018 and premiered on September 30, 2018 on CBS.[2]
